## Monthly Lunar Timing Ritual
**Week 1 — New → Waxing Crescent (Hero)**  
Set intention. Take first action.  
**Week 2 — First Quarter → Waxing Gibbous (Hero)**  
Face challenge. Refine work.  
**Week 3 — Full → Waning Gibbous (Feminine)**  
See truth. Release burden.  
**Week 4 — Last Quarter → Dark Moon (Feminine)**  
Rest. Heal. Listen.

